snippet.title: The Silent Social Deduction Game: Jack & Detectives Trailer
snippet.description:
Jack the Ripper is hiding among us. Can you find him? 

This is a turn-based detection game, but with some twists that make it unique. No talking. No player elimination. Ten minutes per game. These rules are simple, but its nuanced mechanics will keep you entertained.

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1949890/_/
